            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232023%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%89%BE%E6%BB%8B%E7%97%85%E6%97%A5%23&amp;extparam=%232023%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%89%BE%E6%BB%8B%E7%97%85%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#2023年世界艾滋病日#</span></a>】①艾滋病由感染艾滋病病毒（HIV）引起，检测结果呈阴性≠没有艾滋；②一起吃饭、握手拥抱不会被感染；③正确使用暴露前预防药，能降低86%-99%的感染风险；④遵循医嘱，坚持治疗。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奋斗]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/23/2022_Struggle_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>关于艾滋病，一起了解👇🏻更好地保护自己！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康中国） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spmjtmj20p00xcgpt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spl8ztj20p00xcwi9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spmquwj20p00xcdk6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spncidj20p00xcn1n.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spn6h0j20p00xctco.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spnd9nj20p00xcdje.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spowvhj20p00xcwjy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spm509j20p00xcq6j.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hke2spom15j20p00xc0wt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
